Title: 013: 95% Accuracy Models, Winning People Over, and Saving Lives with Damian Mingle
Description:
In this episode of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with Chief Data Scientist Damian R Mingle. You will learn how to build models with 95% accuracy rates, know the 3 top tips on quick wins and winning people over; and get ideas on how to save lives with data science.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/13
